<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 12:12:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>极右翼、仇视同性恋的以色列联盟议员调整政府预算以援助以色列加沙边境社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/far-right-coalition-mk-redirects-govt-budget-to-aid-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-6682-d326-a39b-669acc190000</link><description>毛兹与其他一些联盟议员一样，鉴于与哈马斯的持续战争而选择牺牲预算，他们认为，在“整个以色列民族都在与残酷的敌人作战”之际，这是必要的举动。反对我们&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/far-right-coalition-mk-redirects-govt-budget-to-aid-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-6682-d326-a39b-669acc190000</guid></item><item><title>“我把孩子们的名字写在他们的身上。至少他们会在埋葬前辨认出他们的身份”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-wrote-my-childrens-names-on-their-bodies-at-least-theyll-identify/0000018b-6640-d8ab-a3eb-6f6a6d3d0000</link><description>警告：图形内容。 “他们告诉我们这里更安全，但轰炸无处不在。昨天他们炸毁了附近的一座建筑物。夜晚非常困难&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-wrote-my-childrens-names-on-their-bodies-at-least-theyll-identify/0000018b-6640-d8ab-a3eb-6f6a6d3d0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其埃尔多安称哈马斯是“解放组织”，而不是恐怖分子，并取消对以色列的访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/turkeys-erdogan-says-hamas-is-liberation-group-not-terrorists-cancels-israel-visit/0000018b-663f-d8ab-a3eb-6f7fd1550000</link><description>在向议会发表的讲话中，土耳其领导人要求以色列停止在约旦河西岸的“定居恐怖”和对加沙的袭击，表示巴勒斯坦人应该“团结起来”实现两国解决方案，并表示西方应该停止“火上浇油”。火&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 11:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/turkeys-erdogan-says-hamas-is-liberation-group-not-terrorists-cancels-israel-visit/0000018b-663f-d8ab-a3eb-6f7fd1550000</guid></item><item><title>“做内塔尼亚胡”将意味着走上自杀之路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/doing-a-netanyahu-will-mean-pursuing-a-suicidal-path/0000018b-664f-d473-a5fb-66cf35010000</link><description>目前尚不清楚为什么西方领导人愿意与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理这样的人合作</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/doing-a-netanyahu-will-mean-pursuing-a-suicidal-path/0000018b-664f-d473-a5fb-66cf35010000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争促使意识形态上对立的以色列团体共同努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-pushes-ideologically-opposed-israeli-groups-to-work-together/0000018b-65f5-d473-a5fb-65fd7f130000</link><description>在 2023 年的大部分时间里，反司法政变组织“武装兄弟姐妹”与极端正统派团体以及内塔尼亚胡政府中代表他们的政客几乎陷入了内战。加沙战争使双方团结起来共同对抗新的敌人</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-pushes-ideologically-opposed-israeli-groups-to-work-together/0000018b-65f5-d473-a5fb-65fd7f130000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯世界开始怀疑：哈马斯对以色列的袭击是否算错了？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-world-begins-to-wonder-did-hamas-miscalculate-with-its-attack-against-israel/0000018b-65c7-d230-a1bf-6df7c9980000</link><description>随着时间的推移，随着破坏的蔓延，约旦河西岸和加沙地带都在质疑哈马斯的所作所为，以及它是否真正符合巴勒斯坦人民的利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-world-begins-to-wonder-did-hamas-miscalculate-with-its-attack-against-israel/0000018b-65c7-d230-a1bf-6df7c9980000</guid></item><item><title>她离开乌克兰前往加沙。现在她必须在两场战争之间做出选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/she-left-ukraine-to-live-in-gaza-now-she-has-to-choose-between-two-wars/0000018b-6299-d230-a1bf-6bb968170000</link><description>埃琳娜·哈米达 (Elena Hamida) 18 年前跟随丈夫来到加沙地带。现在她的家人和另外两个人聚集在加沙北部，这是她热爱的土地</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 09:48:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/she-left-ukraine-to-live-in-gaza-now-she-has-to-choose-between-two-wars/0000018b-6299-d230-a1bf-6bb968170000</guid></item><item><title>真主党主席会见黎巴嫩哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织领导人，讨论“加沙真正胜利”的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/hezbollah-chief-meets-with-hamas-islamic-jihad-leaders-in-lebanon-talk-gaza-victory/0000018b-65ac-d288-afef-f5fc701d0000</link><description>这次会议召开之际，以色列和黎巴嫩激进组织之间的紧张关系加剧，以色列北部边境的战斗有可能进一步升级，目前已经造成六名以色列士兵和一名平民死亡，据报道还有 40 名真主党成员死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 07:49:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/hezbollah-chief-meets-with-hamas-islamic-jihad-leaders-in-lebanon-talk-gaza-victory/0000018b-65ac-d288-afef-f5fc701d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道反犹太主义激增，美国犹太人在以色列与哈马斯战争的恐惧气氛中面临暴力威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-25/ty-article/antisemitism-spikes-and-u-s-jews-face-violence-amid-climate-of-fear-over-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-65a7-d288-afef-f5ff0cc00000</link><description>反诽谤联盟表示，哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，他们总共追踪到了 193 起反犹太主义事件，其中在美国增加了 21%； ADL 极端主义中心副总裁表示，“感觉就像纯粹的恐慌模式”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 07:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-25/ty-article/antisemitism-spikes-and-u-s-jews-face-violence-amid-climate-of-fear-over-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-65a7-d288-afef-f5ff0cc00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯向埃拉特发射火箭；土耳其埃尔多安称赞哈马斯为“解放组织”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-syrian-military-targets-biden-israel-will-decide-about-gaza-ground-op/0000018b-6479-d473-a5fb-64f9518e0000</link><description>以色列军队称伊朗通过情报共享帮助哈马斯 ■ 哈马斯高级指挥官在加沙地带被杀 ■ 真主党纳斯鲁拉在黎巴嫩会见伊斯兰圣战组织和哈马斯领导人 ■ 红新月会报告以色列在杰宁空袭造成两人死亡 ■ 加沙再度发射火箭弹 ■ 八名叙利亚人叙利亚官方媒体报道，以色列对军事阵地的空袭造成军事人员死亡 ■ 以色列确认在叙利亚发动袭击 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：5,300 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，18,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 04:33:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-syrian-military-targets-biden-israel-will-decide-about-gaza-ground-op/0000018b-6479-d473-a5fb-64f9518e0000</guid></item><item><title>疏忽大意的内塔尼亚胡为政治生存而战，拒绝面对以色列公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-battles-for-survival-as-the-head-of-israels-endless-fiasco-government/0000018b-6344-ddfd-a59f-e3e43f800000</link><description>在战争最激烈的时期，内塔尼亚胡已经在为第二天做准备，并试图操纵调查委员会。他还没有鼓起勇气面对以色列媒体，但却花了至少一半的时间来确保他的王位稳固</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-battles-for-survival-as-the-head-of-israels-endless-fiasco-government/0000018b-6344-ddfd-a59f-e3e43f800000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-63ec-d230-a1bf-6bfd34d30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 23:03:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-63ec-d230-a1bf-6bfd34d30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙的地面入侵将会发生。何时以及如何取决于拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ground-invasion-of-gaza-will-happen-the-when-and-how-depends-on-biden/0000018b-6344-d288-afef-f3dc404a0000</link><description>美国总统正在给以色列时间——如果以色列做得正确的话——但是，在 10 月 7 日之后，内塔尼亚胡不再相信以色列国防军的能力。加沙地面行动可能会被搁置几天以上</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 21:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ground-invasion-of-gaza-will-happen-the-when-and-how-depends-on-biden/0000018b-6344-d288-afef-f3dc404a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长向人质家属施压，要求其取消与联合国秘书长的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pressured-families-of-hostages-to-cancel-meeting-with-un-secretary-general/0000018b-6374-d473-a5fb-67fd89090000</link><description>在联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯表示哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击“并非凭空发生”后，伊莱·科恩取消了与安东尼奥·古特雷斯的会面。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pressured-families-of-hostages-to-cancel-meeting-with-un-secretary-general/0000018b-6374-d473-a5fb-67fd89090000</guid></item><item><title>在摧毁哈马斯之前释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-the-hostages-comes-before-destroying-hamas/0000018b-62e0-d473-a5fb-66e9382d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-the-hostages-comes-before-destroying-hamas/0000018b-62e0-d473-a5fb-66e9382d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府也正在放弃经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-government-is-abandoning-the-economy-too/0000018b-6306-ddfd-a59f-e3e6dacb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 20:18:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-government-is-abandoning-the-economy-too/0000018b-6306-ddfd-a59f-e3e6dacb0000</guid></item><item><title>释放以色列人质的言论被政府官员视为损害以色列利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-remarks-were-seen-by-government-as-damaging-to-israeli-interests/0000018b-628c-d288-afef-f2dc7ad60000</link><description>约切韦德·利夫希茨 (Yocheved Lifshitz) 声称她“获得了医疗护理”并“在被囚禁期间得到了良好的待遇”，这让官员们担心，这可能会损害国际社会释放剩余人质的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 18:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-remarks-were-seen-by-government-as-damaging-to-israeli-interests/0000018b-628c-d288-afef-f2dc7ad60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人猛烈抨击联合国秘书长称哈马斯袭击“并非凭空发生”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-slams-un-secretary-general-for-saying-hamas-attack-did-not-occur-in-a-vacuum/0000018b-6279-d230-a1bf-6bf965790000</link><description>以色列联盟和反对派成员在社交媒体上严厉谴责联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯为哈马斯的暴行辩护，一些人要求他辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 18:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-slams-un-secretary-general-for-saying-hamas-attack-did-not-occur-in-a-vacuum/0000018b-6279-d230-a1bf-6bf965790000</guid></item><item><title>我们可以从被释放的哈马斯人质约切韦德·利夫什茨身上学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-24/ty-article/.highlight/what-we-can-learn-from-released-hamas-hostage-yocheved-lifshitz/0000018b-6282-d288-afef-f2dac6180000</link><description>约切维德·利夫希茨刚刚经历了世上很少有人能够理解的创伤。尤其是在作为一个自由女性的最初几天，尤其是当她拾起生活中剩下的碎片时，我们不应该评判她处理它的方式</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 17:40:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-24/ty-article/.highlight/what-we-can-learn-from-released-hamas-hostage-yocheved-lifshitz/0000018b-6282-d288-afef-f2dac6180000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯敦促国际社会对哈马斯袭击表示愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/blinken-urges-world-leaders-to-express-outrage-over-hamas-attacks-after-un-controversy/0000018b-626e-d230-a1bf-6bff23fd0000</link><description>“我们谁也无法想象他们所经历的噩梦。美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在谈到人质家属时表示，这是任何家庭都不应该忍受的事情，其中​​几人出席了一次罕见的联合国安理会部长级会议</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 16:53:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/blinken-urges-world-leaders-to-express-outrage-over-hamas-attacks-after-un-controversy/0000018b-626e-d230-a1bf-6bff23fd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>